exceptions.exn: In environment n : nat l : seq expr Unable to unify "uniq (mkseq ?M2366 ?M2367) = true" with "uniq [seq v <- iota 0 (size l) | ~~ is_const (nth (Cst 0) l v) n] = true".

original: intros n l. unfold index_not_const. apply mkseq_uniq. intros i j Hi Hj Heq. unfold mkseq. simpl. apply sub_inj. rewrite mem_filter in Hi, Hj. move/andP: Hi => [Hini _]. move/andP: Hj => [Hinj _]. by rewrite Hini Hinj Heq.
